#: ../../source/blog/cp_benchmark.md:11
msgid "Long-Context Attention Benchmark"
msgstr "长上下文注意力基准测试"

#: ../../source/blog/cp_benchmark.md:13
msgid "**From Kernel Efficiency to Distributed Scalability**"
msgstr "**从内核效率到分布式可扩展性**"

#: ../../source/blog/cp_benchmark.md:15
msgid ""
"To evaluate the performance and flexibility of `Flex-Flash-Attention` "
"(`FFA`) kernels and to validate the distributed scalability of "
"`MagiAttention` for ultra-long, heterogeneous-mask training, we benchmark "
"throughput on modern GPUs (e.g., Hopper and Blackwell) for both kernels and "
"distributed attention modules in forward and backward passes across diverse "
"mask patterns (standard and irregular), against state-of-the-art kernel- and"
" distributed-level baselines."
msgstr ""
"为评估 `Flex-Flash-Attention` (`FFA`) 内核的性能和灵活性，并验证 `MagiAttention` "
"在超长、异构掩码训练中的分布式可扩展性，我们在现代 GPU（如 Hopper 和 "
"Blackwell）上对内核和分布式注意力模块在前向和反向传播中跨多种掩码模式（标准和不规则）进行吞吐量基准测试，并与最先进的内核级和分布式级基线进行对比。"

